}
```

### 2. **ListItem Component Structure** (`src/components/list/list_item/list_item.tsx`)

The ListItem component already implements basic tooltip functionality:
- **For date accessories** (lines 84-86): Uses native HTML `title` attribute to show full date string on hover
- **Accessory rendering** (lines 54-96): Maps through accessories and renders:
  - Tag accessories (with background color styling)
  - Text/icon accessories
  - Date accessories (with formatted relative date display)

Key insight: The component uses the native `title` attribute for dates, but does NOT have custom tooltip styling. Your Tooltip component should provide enhanced visual feedback compared to the browser default.

### 3. **Design Tokens** (`src/styles/_tokens.scss`)

**Z-index values:**
- `$z-dropdown: 100;` - For tooltips attached to list items
- `$z-search-dropdown: 110;`
- `$z-hud: 120;`

**Transitions:**
- `$transition-fast: 80ms;` - Good for tooltip fade-in
- `$transition-normal: 150ms;` - Standard for animations
- `$transition-slow: 250ms;`

**Colors & Styling:**
- `$color-surface: #232325;` - Tooltip background
- `$color-text-primary: #e5e5ea;` - Primary text
- `$text-600: rgba($color-text-primary, 0.6);` - Secondary text
- `$border-100: rgba($color-text-primary, 0.1);`
- `$shadow-popover: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45), 0 1px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);`

**Typography:**
- `$font-xs: 11px;` - Good for tooltip text (similar to accessory-text)
- `$font-sm: 12px;`

**Spacing:**
- `$space-1: 4px;`
- `$space-2: 8px;`

### 4. **Existing Tooltip/Title Pattern**

No dedicated tooltip component exists yet. However, the codebase shows:
- ListItem uses native `title` attribute for date accessories (line 85: `title={accessory.date.toLocaleString()}`)
- No custom tooltip styling or positioning currently in place

### 5. **Positioning & Layout Patterns** 

Based on existing dropdown implementations:

**search_dropdown.scss pattern:**
```scss
.search-dropdown__menu {
  position: absolute;
  top: calc(100% + $space-2);
  right: 0;
  background-color: $color-surface;
  border: 1px solid $border-100;
  border-radius: $radius-lg;
  box-shadow: $shadow-popover;
  z-index: $z-search-dropdown;
  animation: search-dropdown-appear $transition-normal ease-out both;
}

@keyframes search-dropdown-appear {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.96) translateY(-4px);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
  }
}
```

**actions_dropdown.scss pattern:**
```scss
.actions-dropdown {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: calc($action-panel-height + $space-2);
  right: $space-2;
  box-shadow: $shadow-popover;
  z-index: $z-dropdown;
  animation: dropdown-appear $transition-normal ease-out both;
}
```

### 6. **ListItem Styles** (`src/components/list/list_item/list_item.scss`)

Key styling context:
- Accessories container uses `display: flex` with gap spacing
- Accessory text uses `font-size: $font-xs` and `color: $text-400`
- List item has `position: relative` (implicit for absolute child positioning)
- Height is `$list-item-height: 40px`

```scss
